# Houdini Documentation Crawler Project Overview

This project is a comprehensive documentation crawler and processor for Houdini-related content, consisting of several key components:

## Core Components

### Documentation Crawlers
- [app.py](mdc:app.py) - Main documentation crawler application
- [app_odforce.py](mdc:app_odforce.py) - Specialized crawler for ODForce forum content
- [chunker.py](mdc:chunker.py) - Utility for chunking large documentation into manageable pieces

### Document Converters
- [pdf_to_markdown_converter.py](mdc:pdf_to_markdown_converter.py) - Converts PDF documentation to Markdown format
- [markdownConverter_OLD.py](mdc:markdownConverter_OLD.py) - Legacy markdown conversion utility

### Dataset Generation
- [optimized_generate_qna_dataset.py](mdc:optimized_generate_qna_dataset.py) - Creates Q&A datasets from processed documentation

## Directory Structure

### Documentation Sources
- `houdini_docs_mkdown/` - Markdown format Houdini documentation
- `houdini_docs_pdf/` - Original PDF format documentation
- `odforce_scrapMD/` - Scraped ODForce forum content
- `markitdown/` - Markdown processing utilities

### Processed Content
- `Chunked_Markdown/` - Documentation split into manageable chunks
- `PDF_to_Markdown/` - Converted PDF documentation
- `qna_dataset/` - Generated Q&A datasets

